The jsonSave functiois can be called:
with an id param => will update the item
without any id   => will create a new item

The save function will validate the fields,
if all is ok, the item is saved.
If not, an error is return to the dojo client in the format:
/* {"error":[{"field":"title","message":"Is a required field"},{"field":"startDate","message":"Is a required field"},{"field":"endDate","message":"Is a required field"},{"field":"priority","message":"Is a required field"}]} */